question: Anna is required to submit a 288-page report. She already finished writing 1/16 of the report. How many pages does she have left to write?
answer:
Anna has already written 1/16 of the report which is 288 pages*1/16 = <<288*1/16=18>>18 pages.
So, she still needs to write 288 pages - 18 pages = <<288-18=270>>270 pages.
#### 270
